  "title": "6723 - Audit Senior / Audit Supervisor / Asst. Audit Manager [Bugis | Mid-Tier Firm | up to $5500]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position: Audit Senior / Audit Supervisor / Assistant Manager</strong><br>\n<strong>Location:</strong> Beach Road<br>\n<strong>Working Days:</strong> Mon - Fri<br>\n<strong>Working Hours:</strong> 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM<br>\n<strong>Salary:</strong> Up to $5,500 (depending on experience &amp; designation)</p>\n<h2><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead and manage audit engagements from planning to finalization, ensuring completion within budget and timelines.</li>\n  <li>Supervise and review work performed by junior staff, ensuring quality and compliance with auditing standards.</li>\n  <li>Develop tailored audit strategies based on client business understanding and risk areas.</li>\n  <li>Maintain and nurture long-term client relationships, managing expectations and identifying business opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Provide technical guidance and contribute to continuous improvement of audit methodologies and firm practices.</li>\n  <li>Participate in staff development, resource planning, recruitment, and internal training initiatives.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><strong>Requirements</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor's Degree in Accountancy or equivalent qualification.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 1–2 years of audit experience for Senior Associate, and 4+ years for Assistant Manager level.</li>\n  <li>Strong technical knowledge of audit standards and ethical principles.</li>\n  <li>Prior experience in handling full audit cycles and supervising teams is preferred for senior roles.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>https://wa.me/6596420989</strong></p>\n<p><strong>WhatsApp: +65 9642 0989 (Han)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Email: supreme.cc.han@gmail.com</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Chaw Chiaw Han, Reg No：R22106723</strong></p>\n<p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd, EA No：14c7279</strong></p>",
